          "type": "text",
          "content": "真臊的无地可入，"
        },
        {
          "type": "annotation",
          "source": "庚",
          "position": "",
          "color": "red",
          "content": "庚"
        },
        {
          "type": "annotation",
          "source": "庚",
          "position": "",
          "color": "red",
          "content": "侧：亦未必真。"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "不知要怎么样才好，回身就要跑，被贾蔷一把揪住道：“别"
        },
